&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;37.5 Hours Per Week&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Doncaster and Bassetlaw Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust seek to recruit an Paediatric Staff Nurse for the Children&#39;s Ambulatory Care Unit at Bassetlaw District General.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Children’s Ambulatory Care Unit is a day time service where patients are referred for Paediatric &lt;strong&gt;assessment by the G.P, ED, Midwife or through open access. Any patients that require admission overnight are&lt;/strong&gt; transferred to the Children’s Ward or Children’s Observation Unit at Doncaster Royal Infirmary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you are a newly qualified Staff Nurse please apply via our Trust Wide advert where you will have the opportunity to specify your area of choice / interest, please email dbth.recruitment@nhs.net for further details.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Matt Timms - Matron - Children&#39;s, matthewtimms@nhs.net, 07795 317499&lt;/p&gt;
